parameters.text: This chart displays the % of SKUs that were SP compliant in the enrolled stores for the country over a period of last 13 months.
This chart displays the % of SKUs that were SP compliant in the enrolled stores for a country in the last month.
This chart displays the % of enrolled stores that were Price compliant for the country over a period of last 13 months.
This chart displays the % of SKUs that were SP compliant in the enrolled stores for Top Customers within a country in the latest month.
This chart displays the % of SKUs that were SP compliant in the enrolled stores across all the Channels in the country in the latest month.
This chart displays the % of 4P, 5P and 6P stores that were Price compliant for the country in the latest month.
This chart displays the % of enrolled stores that were Price compliant across all the Channels in the country in the latest month.
This chart displays the % of enrolled stores that were Price compliant for the last month.
This chart displays the % of MT enrolled stores that were Price compliant across all the Product categories in the country in the latest month.
This chart displays the % of enrolled stores that were Price compliant in different sales regions of the country in the latest month.
This chart displays the % of SKUs that were SP compliant in 4P, 5P and 6P stores in the country in the latest month.
This chart displays the % of SKUs that were SP compliant in enrolled stores in different sales regions of the country in the latest month.
This chart displays the % of SKUs that were SP compliant in MT enrolled stores across all the Product categories in the country in the latest month.
This chart lists all the audited SKUs in the country, the % of enrolled stores that they were SP compliant in in the latest month, and the variance from the previous month.
This chart displays the % of enrolled stores for Top Customers within a country which were Price Compliant in the latest month.
